			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "loadlevel SCL_Main_A\r\noe debugbook > Go to region > Act 2 > HAV > Isobels room\r\nSpeak with isobel and accept protection spell.\r\nAnother dialogue will follow. Protect Isobel.\r\nkillcombat\r\nteleport S_MOO_KethericHound\r\nFollow through with dialogue and accept to deal with the goblins.\r\ncrimes -disable\r\nteleport S_MOO_KethericHound\r\ninteract with Hound, let her sniff you\r\noe mooassault_alive\r\nthis will trigger moonrise assault event\r\nteleport S_MOO_KethericHound"
				},
